item.title: CVE-2016-9605|2024-08-06T02:59:02.710Z -- the%20cobbler%20project -- cobbler
item.description: A flaw was found in cobbler software component version 2.6.11-1. It suffers from an invalid parameter validation vulnerability, leading the arbitrary file reading. The flaw is triggered by navigating to a vulnerable URL via cobbler-web on a default installation.
